data.description: This 2 bed 1 bath may be deceiving from the outside. There is a large spacious stepdown room that could be used as an entertainment room, or even another bedroom. There is also an added room that is currently being used as the laundry room, and has a glass slider out to the backyard. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, gas range, and built in cabinets for pantry or storage use.  Hot tub stays with the home, and is in good working condition. Many plants and shrubs throughout with a wide variety of fruit trees from apple, cherry, fig, apricot, peach, to pomegranate. Back yard is fully fenced, with two larger side driveways, one with an aluminum detached carport. Come sit and enjoy the neighborhood from the front covered deck, with beautifully arranged foliage and plants for privacy.
